  "preFix": {
    "title": "Calligraphy warm-up exercises",
    "subtitle": "The strokes and drills that prepare the hand before writing a calligraphy session",
    "excerpt": "Broad-edge and pointed-pen calligraphy both benefit from five minutes of warm-up strokes before writing text. These drills establish consistent nib angle, ink flow, and muscle memory, so the first letters of the session are as clean as the last.",
    "sourceNotes": "Edward Johnston, Writing and Illuminating and Lettering (1906), chapter on practice methods. Internet Archive: https://archive.org/details/writingillumina00john. Johnston recommends beginning each practice session with a set of foundational strokes to establish the hand before working on letterforms.",
    "body": {
      "type": "doc",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Cold hand, inconsistent ink, uncertain nib angle: these are the three main reasons why the first five minutes of a calligraphy session are often the worst. Warm-up exercises address all three systematically. They are not a ritual or a delay: they are what prepares a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "consistent nib angle",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                  "attrs": {
                    "termId": "cmpqsioj20002esv4tvhwsrjz"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "text": " and a steady ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "pull-stroke",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                  "attrs": {
                    "termId": "cmpqsioia0001esv4vfs3b0vr"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "text": " before the page that matters.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "What you need",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "suppliesCard",
          "attrs": {
            "items": [
              {
                "name": "Mitchell Roundhand nib, 3 (broad-edge warm-up)",
                "slug": "nib-mitchell-roundhand-3",
                "isOptional": true
              },
              {
                "name": "Nikko G nib (pointed-pen warm-up)",
                "slug": "nib-nikko-g",
                "isOptional": true
              },
              {
